    <section id="fs-id2849499" type="problems-exercises" class="problems-exercises"><title>Problems &amp; Exercises</title><exercise id="fs-id2626487" type="problems-exercises"><problem id="fs-id2072145"><para id="import-auto-id2099909">Indicate whether the magnetic field created in each of the three situations shown in <link target-id="import-auto-id1917466"/> is into or out of the page on the left and right of the current.</para><figure id="import-auto-id1917466"><media id="import-auto-id1416918" alt="Figure a shows current I running from bottom to top. Figure b shows an electron moving with velocity v from bottom to top. Figure c shows current I running from top to bottom.">
