 <para id="import-auto-id1508672">What are the directions of the currents in the loop and coils shown in <link target-id="import-auto-id2156525"/>?</para><figure id="import-auto-id2156525"><media id="import-auto-id2017025" alt="Figure a shows the magnetic field into the page in the middle of a loop. Figure b shows the magnetic field within a coil running from left to right. Figure c shows B running from right to left within a coil.">
